Agar Inheritance me child ne implement kaar rakha hai serealizable interface
but parent ne nahi then es case me 4 cearios bante hai 

1.Hum  child ko serealize kara sakte hai kyui Object class ne bhi implement nahi 
  kaar rakha hota serealizable interface but sare objet ki parent class hoti hai vo
 
2.At time of Serealization JVM check karta hai ki koi variable jo non serializable(yani parent class se)
  area(zone) se aaya ho then JVM us variable ki Value ignore kaar deta hai aur aapni tafar se koi default
  value assign kaar deta hai 
  
 3.At time of Desirealization JVM check if any parent is non serializable then JVM give its instance variable values from that class 
   to the Object that we get from the deserialization and 
initiate  instance control flow that follow 3 step
   1.Identification of Instance Member
   2.Execution of Instant Variable Assingnment
   3.Execution of no argument constructor of non serializable  parent class
   
 4.Every non Serilizable parent class ko humesha  no agrs constructor contain karna 
   jaruri hai nahi tho throw hogi Invalid class Exception